Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In today's fast -paced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,tech landscape efficiency scheme,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,enter programmatic tool calling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Claude a game changer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,for developers and tech
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,enthusiasts alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This feature allows Claude
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,execute code that interacts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,with tools directly, slashing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,latency and token usage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine not having
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to deal with those
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,annoying round trips for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,every tool invocation sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,liberating, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Programmatic tool calling is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,particularly useful for multi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-tool workflows where every
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,millisecond counts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the model to process
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,each tool call.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This feature allows you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to filter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or process data before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,sending it to the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,model's context window.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This means you can
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,streamline your
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,operations significantly, but remember
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to have
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,code execution tools enabled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in your
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,environment for this to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,practical example, say you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.61,0:00:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,are aggregating sales
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,data from different regions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.47,0:00:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,With programmatic tool calling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you can query a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,database directly and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.89,0:00:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,get results in a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This not only saves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,time but also ensures
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that your data is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,accurate and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,up to date.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus the output is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:00:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,structured in JSON format,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,making it easy to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.57,0:01:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,tech officials, let's dive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,into some crucial specs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The maximum token limit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,for responses using
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,this feature is 4
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,,096 tokens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This allows for extensive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,data handling without compromising
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, don't forget that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,this capability is available
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,via the Claude API
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and Microsoft Foundry,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,which makes integration seamless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ensure that you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.84,0:01:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,adhere to the standard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,data retention
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,policies as programmatic tool
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,calling is not covered
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,by zero data retention
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,policies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So there you have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it, programmatic tool calling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is set to revolutionize
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,how we interact with
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,tools
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in Claude, enhancing efficiency
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a developer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,or just a tech
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,enthusiast,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,this feature is definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,worth exploring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Embrace the future of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,coding with Claude and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,let
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,efficiency reign supreme.
